# ORIG TITLE    Monty and Fred make a good couple in Golf’s Hall of Fame . 
# ORIG CONTENT  Scot Colin Montgomerie has been inducted into Golf’s Hall of Fame at a ceremony in St Augustine, Florida. Although Monty never won a major his contribution to the sport is significant. He won eight Orders of Merit, seven of them in succession, a fact that illustrates his dominance on the European circuit between 1993 and 1999. US clubber Fred Couples, former world No.1 and the 1992 US Masters Champion, was also honored and described the moment as the “coolest night of his life.” . 
